{"word":"νηέω","slug":"νηέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n70630\" key=\"nhe/w\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">νη-έω</orth>, <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Dor.\">Dor.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">νᾱέω</orth>, older form of <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">νέω</foreign> (c), <sense id=\"n70630.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">heap, pile up,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἐπ᾽ αὐτῶν νήησαν ξύλα πολλά</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:19:64\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">19.64</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; of a funeral pile, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">μενοεικέα νήεον ὕλην</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:23:139\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">23.139</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">περὶ δὲ δρατᾲ σώματα νήει</foreign> ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:169\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">169</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πῦρ τ᾽ εὖ νηῆσαι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:15:322\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">15.322</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; also <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐπ᾽ ἀ