l.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.358</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>:—in <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Med.\">Med.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">νῆα ἅλις</foreign> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">χρυσοῦ—νηησάσθω</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">let him pile his</tr_> ship with gold enough, ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:137\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">137</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:279\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">279</biblScope></bibl>. [Sts. corrupted to <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">νηνέω,</foreign> q.v.]</sense> </entryFree>"}]}